com.oym.indoor.routing

Class IndoorRouting

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.oym.indoor.Indoor
      • com.oym.indoor.routing.IndoorRouting

  • public class IndoorRouting
extends Indoor
    This class includes all the interface with the server, its calls and its callbacks. It extends Indoor by adding it routing functionalities.
